Text: Well it is the very rare edition which you cant find anywhere in the Internet. If you are a windows collector then it is a treasure for you. :)

A valid serial can be found here: http://forums.mydigitallife.info/threads/5459-Windows-XP-Starter-Edition?p=66589&viewfull=1#post66589
